{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1344,"text":"(Aquatic noises)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8811,"text":"So this video was taken"},{"time":10714,"text":"at Aquarius undersea laboratory"},{"time":13146,"text":"four miles off the coast of Key Largo,"},{"time":14999,"text":"about 60 feet below the surface."},{"time":17577,"text":"NASA uses this extreme environment"},{"time":19301,"text":"to train astronauts and aquanauts,"},{"time":21725,"text":"and last year, they invited us along for the ride."},{"time":25087,"text":"All the footage was taken from our open ROV,"},{"time":27971,"text":"which is a robot that we built in our garage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32458,"text":"So ROV stands for Remote Operated Vehicle,"},{"time":36026,"text":"which in our case means our little robot"},{"time":37553,"text":"sends live video"},{"time":39817,"text":"across that ultra-thin tether"},{"time":41735,"text":"back to the computer topside."},{"time":44163,"text":"It's open source, meaning we publish"},{"time":46141,"text":"and share all of our design files"},{"time":48186,"text":"and all of our code online,"},{"time":49694,"text":"allowing anyone to modify"},{"time":51728,"text":"or improve or change the design."},{"time":54077,"text":"It's built with mostly off-the-shelf parts"},{"time":56380,"text":"and costs about 1,000 times cheaper"},{"time":58215,"text":"than the ROVs James Cameron used"},{"time":60094,"text":"to explore the Titanic."},{"time":63699,"text":"So ROVs aren't new."},{"time":65909,"text":"They've been around for decades."},{"time":67617,"text":"Scientists use ROVs to explore the oceans."},{"time":70653,"text":"Oil and gas companies use them for exploration"},{"time":73472,"text":"and construction."},{"time":75019,"text":"What we've built isn't unique."},{"time":77781,"text":"It's how we've built it that's really unique."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80655,"text":"So I want to give you a quick story\nof how it got started."},{"time":83636,"text":"So a few years ago, my friend Eric and I"},{"time":85907,"text":"decided we wanted to explore this underwater cave"},{"time":88107,"text":"in the foothills of the Sierras."},{"time":89965,"text":"We had heard this story about lost gold"},{"time":91868,"text":"from a Gold Rush-era robbery,\nand we wanted to go up there."},{"time":94386,"text":"Unfortunately, we didn't have any money"},{"time":96044,"text":"and we didn't have any tools to do it."},{"time":97867,"text":"So Eric had an initial design idea for a robot,"},{"time":101067,"text":"but we didn't have all the parts figured out,"},{"time":103840,"text":"so we did what anybody would do in our situation:"},{"time":106052,"text":"we asked the Internet for help."},{"time":108090,"text":"More specifically, we created this website,"},{"time":110622,"text":"openROV.com, and shared \nour intentions and our plans"},{"time":113517,"text":"For the first few months, it was just Eric and I"},{"time":115907,"text":"talking back to each other on the forums,"},{"time":118437,"text":"but pretty soon, we started to get feedback"},{"time":120525,"text":"from makers and hobbyists,"},{"time":122368,"text":"and then actually professional ocean engineers"},{"time":124362,"text":"who had some suggestions for what we should do."},{"time":127894,"text":"We kept working on it. We learned a lot."},{"time":129658,"text":"We kept prototyping, and eventually,"},{"time":131683,"text":"we decided we wanted to go \nto the cave. We were ready."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134402,"text":"So about that time, our little expedition\nbecame quite a story,"},{"time":137842,"text":"and it got picked up in The New York Times."},{"time":139863,"text":"And we were pretty much just overwhelmed"},{"time":141675,"text":"with interest from people who wanted a kit"},{"time":143458,"text":"that they could build this open ROV themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145979,"text":"So we decided to put the project on Kickstarter,"},{"time":149268,"text":"and when we did,"},{"time":150500,"text":"we raised our funding goal in about two hours,"},{"time":152575,"text":"and all of a sudden, \nhad this money to make these kits."},{"time":155780,"text":"But then we had to learn how to make them."},{"time":157975,"text":"I mean, we had to learn small batch manufacturing."},{"time":160140,"text":"So we quickly learned that our garage"},{"time":163400,"text":"was not big enough to hold our growing operation."},{"time":166079,"text":"But we were able to do it, we got all the kits made,"},{"time":168235,"text":"thanks a lot to TechShop,\nwhich was a big help to us,"},{"time":170942,"text":"and we shipped these kits all over the world"},{"time":173927,"text":"just before Christmas of last year,"},{"time":175756,"text":"so it was just a few months ago."},{"time":177538,"text":"But we're already starting to get video"},{"time":179446,"text":"and photos back from all over the world,"},{"time":181044,"text":"including this shot from under the ice in Antarctica."},{"time":184074,"text":"We've also learned the penguins love robots."},{"time":187474,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":189487,"text":"So we're still publishing all the designs online,"},{"time":192655,"text":"encouraging anyone to build these themselves."},{"time":194773,"text":"That's the only way that we could have done this."},{"time":197176,"text":"By being open source, we've created"},{"time":198835,"text":"this distributed R&amp;D network,"},{"time":201099,"text":"and we're moving faster than\nany venture-backed counterpart."},{"time":204895,"text":"But the actual robot is really only half the story."},{"time":208100,"text":"The real potential, the long term potential,"},{"time":210596,"text":"is with this community of DIY ocean explorers"},{"time":213273,"text":"that are forming all over the globe."},{"time":215669,"text":"What can we discover"},{"time":217203,"text":"when there's thousands of these devices"},{"time":219107,"text":"roaming the seas?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221153,"text":"So you're probably all wondering: the cave."},{"time":223429,"text":"Did you find the gold?"},{"time":225255,"text":"Well, we didn't find any gold,"},{"time":226807,"text":"but we decided that what we found\nwas much more valuable."},{"time":230036,"text":"It was the glimpse into a potential future"},{"time":232508,"text":"for ocean exploration."},{"time":234183,"text":"It's something that's not limited to\nthe James Camerons of the world,"},{"time":237093,"text":"but something that we're all participating in."},{"time":239688,"text":"It's an underwater world"},{"time":241021,"text":"we're all exploring together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243532,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245707,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}